name: Candy Heart Tea Light Set
description: Tiny heart-shaped tealights in an array of pastel colors are the very essence of innocence and romance! Sweetly reminiscent of the Valentine’s Day candy classic, these votives fill the air with an alluring sugared-fruit fragrance. Glass holders; palm wax candles. 7” x 4 1/2” x 1” high. Set of 6

name: Heat Locket Necklace
description: This super-stylish double-drop necklace gets its glamour from loads of sparkling rings and charms, and it even has a secret! Open the pretty lacework locket to reveal a stash spot— perfect for keeping a treasured photo or teeny-tiny trinket right next to your heart! Alloy metal. 28” long. Locket holds a 3/4” x 3/4” photo.

name: Vivatar 35mm camera
description:
When it’s time to record your next snorkeling adventure, the Vivitar® Mariner Underwater 35mm Camera will do the trick. 
Taking shots of that extraordinary coral reef or those schools of rainbow-colored fish has never been easier. 
Waterproof up to 10 feet, the Vivitar Mariner features a focus-free, 28 millimeter, f9.0 lens with shutter speeds of up to 1/125 second, which means you won’t have to worry about letting that big one get away while you’re trying to focus. 
And when you’re out of the water and back on the beach ready to relax, this Vivitar will be ready for you. 
Just take the camera out of its underwater housing, and you’ll be ready to shoot the sunsets or catch some great beach volleyball action on film. 
The Vivitar Mariner Underwater Camera is an ideal 35mm camera for the aspiring vacationer. 
Features: 
35mm Camera 
Focus Free 
Built-in-Flash 
Easy Film Loading 
Waterproof to 10 Feet 
Removable Housing
